1
00:00:07,460 --> 00:00:10,180
♪Hush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pond♪

2
00:00:11,180 --> 00:00:14,140
♪A shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chest♪

3
00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:16,820
♪I would shield you♪

4
00:00:16,820 --> 00:00:19,820
♪From this cruel wind and frost♪

5
00:00:22,220 --> 00:00:24,700
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

6
00:00:25,660 --> 00:00:28,500
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

7
00:00:29,260 --> 00:00:30,820
♪This lingering afterglow♪

8
00:00:30,820 --> 00:00:34,660
♪Holds the image
of our very first glance♪

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:39,340
♪I borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze window♪

10
00:00:39,700 --> 00:00:43,660
♪Tailoring moonlight
into your luminous gown♪

11
00:00:44,140 --> 00:00:50,060
♪Severing the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendor♪

12
00:00:50,620 --> 00:00:54,220
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

13
00:00:54,460 --> 00:00:57,940
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

14
00:00:58,900 --> 00:01:04,900
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

15
00:01:05,260 --> 00:01:11,740
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:11,780 --> 00:01:16,740
=Episode 19=

17
00:01:17,900 --> 00:01:18,580
Yunzhuo,

18
00:01:18,580 --> 00:01:20,300
you hail from the capital.

19
00:01:20,620 --> 00:01:21,740
Surely you've seen more of the world.

20
00:01:22,180 --> 00:01:22,980
Any brilliant insights

21
00:01:22,980 --> 00:01:24,180
to share?

22
00:01:24,700 --> 00:01:26,180
I'm just a businessman.

23
00:01:26,460 --> 00:01:27,540
No brilliant insights here.

24
00:01:28,700 --> 00:01:29,580
(As I see it, you're a businessman)

25
00:01:29,580 --> 00:01:30,940
(with some serious backing.)

26
00:01:31,380 --> 00:01:32,060
(It was you)

27
00:01:32,060 --> 00:01:33,620
(who insisted I meet Miss Xue,)

28
00:01:33,620 --> 00:01:35,220
(luring me with Xianquan Tavern.)

29
00:01:35,380 --> 00:01:36,540
(You even dared to boast)

30
00:01:36,660 --> 00:01:37,620
(that you could get Gambiered Silk)

31
00:01:37,620 --> 00:01:39,020
(back on the imperial tribute list.)

32
00:01:39,540 --> 00:01:41,420
(No way you've got nothing shady)

33
00:01:42,060 --> 00:01:43,180
(going on.)

34
00:01:44,740 --> 00:01:45,420
Isn't Feng City about to hold

35
00:01:45,420 --> 00:01:47,140
a major event soon?

36
00:01:47,300 --> 00:01:48,340
While the crowds are here,

37
00:01:48,500 --> 00:01:49,140
we could spread the news

38
00:01:49,140 --> 00:01:52,100
about Prince Ning's rebellion
far and wide.

39
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:53,620
What are you thinking?

40
00:01:53,940 --> 00:01:55,300
Raising an army for rebellion

41
00:01:55,380 --> 00:01:56,540
is no small matter.

42
00:01:56,900 --> 00:01:58,180
Once this news gets out,

43
00:01:58,700 --> 00:02:00,140
if Prince Ning marches his troops,

44
00:02:00,140 --> 00:02:01,020
then Feng City

45
00:02:01,020 --> 00:02:02,620
will be slaughtered down
to the last person.

46
00:02:03,140 --> 00:02:03,980
Exactly.

47
00:02:03,980 --> 00:02:04,980
The fewer people

48
00:02:04,980 --> 00:02:06,500
who know about this, the better.

49
00:02:06,620 --> 00:02:07,380
Right now, our priority

50
00:02:07,380 --> 00:02:08,620
is to get this information
to His Majesty

51
00:02:08,620 --> 00:02:09,780
as quickly as possible.

52
00:02:10,740 --> 00:02:11,660
Miss Xue,

53
00:02:11,660 --> 00:02:12,620
while you were in the capital,

54
00:02:12,620 --> 00:02:14,140
did you never get a chance
to see the emperor?

55
00:02:14,500 --> 00:02:15,980
If I could have reached His Majesty,

56
00:02:16,300 --> 00:02:17,100
why would I

57
00:02:17,340 --> 00:02:19,220
have fled all the way
from the capital back to Feng City?

58
00:02:19,580 --> 00:02:21,540
With your status as
the Chancellor's granddaughter,

59
00:02:21,540 --> 00:02:23,180
you still had no way
to get word to the emperor?

60
00:02:23,500 --> 00:02:24,700
Right now, Prince Ning

61
00:02:24,700 --> 00:02:26,140
already wields power
that eclipses the whole court.

62
00:02:27,500 --> 00:02:28,620
That means

63
00:02:28,900 --> 00:02:29,740
the current sovereign

64
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:31,380
is nothing more than a puppet.

65
00:02:40,220 --> 00:02:41,740
Why have you all gone quiet?

66
00:02:43,220 --> 00:02:45,300
Judging from
what Miss Xue has gone through,

67
00:02:45,300 --> 00:02:46,900
the situation we're facing now

68
00:02:46,900 --> 00:02:48,740
is far worse than we imagined.

69
00:02:48,740 --> 00:02:49,980
In the imperial court,

70
00:02:49,980 --> 00:02:51,180
factions band together for private gain,

71
00:02:51,180 --> 00:02:52,460
and one man rules with absolute power.

72
00:02:52,460 --> 00:02:53,220
Prince Ning

73
00:02:53,220 --> 00:02:54,700
is no longer plotting rebellion
in the shadows.

74
00:02:55,100 --> 00:02:56,420
He's about to usurp the throne openly.

75
00:02:57,460 --> 00:02:58,460
He definitely wants

76
00:02:58,780 --> 00:03:00,380
to get his hands on this edict.

77
00:03:01,380 --> 00:03:03,500
And he'll announce to the world

78
00:03:04,780 --> 00:03:06,980
that Chancellor Sun was scheming,

79
00:03:06,980 --> 00:03:08,740
hiding the edict for himself.

80
00:03:09,340 --> 00:03:10,060
What?

81
00:03:10,420 --> 00:03:12,180
Not only did Prince Ning
harm my grandfather,

82
00:03:12,380 --> 00:03:13,380
but now he wants to smear his name

83
00:03:13,380 --> 00:03:14,820
and destroy his lifelong honor?

84
00:03:14,980 --> 00:03:15,540
Perhaps,

85
00:03:16,020 --> 00:03:17,340
this was all part

86
00:03:17,780 --> 00:03:19,620
of Prince Ning's scheme
right from the very start.

87
00:03:19,860 --> 00:03:20,940
The edict is fake,

88
00:03:20,940 --> 00:03:23,100
so there was no need
to give it to Miss Xue.

89
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:24,420
As Miss Xue

90
00:03:24,420 --> 00:03:26,300
didn't hand the edict
over to the emperor,

91
00:03:26,300 --> 00:03:27,580
but instead fled with it

92
00:03:27,580 --> 00:03:28,620
all the way here,

93
00:03:28,620 --> 00:03:30,220
naturally, some people
would start to wonder

94
00:03:30,220 --> 00:03:32,620
if this fake edict
could actually be real.

95
00:03:32,620 --> 00:03:34,620
They'd start to suspect
whether the edict

96
00:03:34,620 --> 00:03:35,820
that put the emperor on the throne

97
00:03:36,100 --> 00:03:37,380
might be a fake.

98
00:03:37,620 --> 00:03:39,820
Exactly. Repeated lies become truth.

99
00:03:40,220 --> 00:03:41,340
Constant dripping wears away the stone.

100
00:03:42,020 --> 00:03:42,540
When Prince Ning

101
00:03:42,540 --> 00:03:44,380
gets his hands on this edict again,

102
00:03:44,820 --> 00:03:46,300
the fake will have become real.

103
00:03:46,780 --> 00:03:47,700
When that happens,

104
00:03:48,060 --> 00:03:49,500
his rebellion will be recast

105
00:03:49,660 --> 00:03:51,620
as the emperor having
taken the throne illegitimately,

106
00:03:52,020 --> 00:03:53,500
and Prince Ning
simply purging the court.

107
00:03:54,380 --> 00:03:55,540
What a wicked scheme!

108
00:03:56,100 --> 00:03:57,020
Prince Ning is playing

109
00:03:57,020 --> 00:03:58,580
an open hand

110
00:03:58,940 --> 00:04:00,140
right under the emperor's nose.

111
00:04:00,580 --> 00:04:01,500
Doesn't the emperor

112
00:04:01,500 --> 00:04:03,140
have any inkling of this at all?

113
00:04:06,540 --> 00:04:08,500
If Prince Ning
dares to act this brazenly,

114
00:04:08,940 --> 00:04:10,940
he must be dead certain
he can pull it off.

115
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:12,300
From the looks of it,

116
00:04:12,300 --> 00:04:13,540
my guess is correct.

117
00:04:13,900 --> 00:04:15,100
The current emperor

118
00:04:15,500 --> 00:04:16,300
has long since been reduced

119
00:04:16,300 --> 00:04:17,500
to nothing but a puppet emperor.

120
00:04:19,740 --> 00:04:20,620
So,

121
00:04:20,980 --> 00:04:23,100
whose side should we take?

122
00:04:25,220 --> 00:04:25,900
Li Yunhe,

123
00:04:25,900 --> 00:04:27,940
you've been muttering to yourself
for ages.

124
00:04:27,940 --> 00:04:29,220
Where's the plan to break this deadlock?

125
00:04:29,620 --> 00:04:30,820
Prince Ning's rebellion

126
00:04:31,220 --> 00:04:32,020
is no longer the same

127
00:04:32,020 --> 00:04:33,900
as dealing with
some run-of-the-mill corrupt official.

128
00:04:34,140 --> 00:04:35,220
For now, our only option

129
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:38,140
is to find a way to get this message
all the way up to the emperor

130
00:04:38,140 --> 00:04:39,100
and gamble that the emperor still has

131
00:04:39,100 --> 00:04:40,220
some loyal men at his disposal.

132
00:04:41,420 --> 00:04:42,900
But with Prince Ning
controlling the court,

133
00:04:43,300 --> 00:04:44,300
even when I was in the capital,

134
00:04:44,300 --> 00:04:45,700
I was utterly powerless to act.

135
00:04:46,180 --> 00:04:46,860
How can we

136
00:04:47,380 --> 00:04:49,300
get a message through now?

137
00:04:49,700 --> 00:04:52,180
This year, Feng City was hit
by devastating floods.

138
00:04:52,780 --> 00:04:54,340
The emperor has already decreed
disaster relief.

139
00:04:54,780 --> 00:04:55,900
In the past few days,

140
00:04:56,220 --> 00:04:58,300
I've seen quite a bit of relief grain

141
00:04:58,300 --> 00:04:59,820
arriving here in Feng City.

142
00:05:00,300 --> 00:05:01,220
If

143
00:05:01,220 --> 00:05:02,820
we can stall for a few more days,

144
00:05:02,820 --> 00:05:04,300
then we might figure out a way

145
00:05:04,980 --> 00:05:06,220
to pass a letter.

146
00:05:07,180 --> 00:05:08,300
Pass a letter?

147
00:05:09,820 --> 00:05:11,540
In a matter of days,

148
00:05:11,540 --> 00:05:14,180
the emperor will indeed
be sending someone to Feng City.

149
00:05:14,580 --> 00:05:16,300
Who? And for what purpose?

150
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:17,500
The Zhou family's Gambiered Silk

151
00:05:17,500 --> 00:05:19,140
has been stripped
of its imperial tribute status.

152
00:05:19,380 --> 00:05:21,700
The emperor will send an envoy
to the Feng City Weaving Bureau

153
00:05:21,700 --> 00:05:23,020
to announce this news,

154
00:05:23,020 --> 00:05:23,740
and incidentally,

155
00:05:23,740 --> 00:05:25,700
to select a new tribute product.

156
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:27,100
Select a new tribute product?

157
00:05:27,620 --> 00:05:28,980
If we could get the Gambiered Silk

158
00:05:29,300 --> 00:05:31,100
reinstated as an imperial tribute,

159
00:05:31,540 --> 00:05:32,260
perhaps

160
00:05:33,020 --> 00:05:34,340
things could take a turn for the better.

161
00:05:34,820 --> 00:05:36,180
And you think with just this scheme

162
00:05:36,180 --> 00:05:38,420
you could get an audience
with the emperor?

163
00:05:38,740 --> 00:05:39,420
Right.

164
00:05:39,620 --> 00:05:41,340
Losing the imperial tribute status

165
00:05:41,340 --> 00:05:42,700
was the emperor's personal decree.

166
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:45,220
Getting back on the list
is almost impossible.

167
00:05:45,380 --> 00:05:45,980
Besides,

168
00:05:46,100 --> 00:05:47,580
how would you even get a letter through?

169
00:05:48,420 --> 00:05:49,500
Exactly. Li Yunhe,

170
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:50,620
it's not that I don't trust you,

171
00:05:50,620 --> 00:05:51,900
but the imperial envoy sent

172
00:05:51,900 --> 00:05:52,620
by the Royal Weaving Bureau

173
00:05:52,620 --> 00:05:54,420
has a chance to meet the emperor,

174
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:55,660
but how do you know

175
00:05:55,660 --> 00:05:56,900
he hasn't already thrown in
his lot with Prince Ning?

176
00:05:56,900 --> 00:05:57,980
When did I ever say

177
00:05:58,380 --> 00:05:59,780
I was going to use a person
to carry the message?

178
00:06:00,100 --> 00:06:00,860
Not a person?

179
00:06:01,380 --> 00:06:02,740
Then what will carry the message?

180
00:06:03,620 --> 00:06:04,420
Tax silver.

181
00:06:04,900 --> 00:06:05,820
Tax silver?

182
00:06:06,820 --> 00:06:08,700
Tax silver indeed concerns
the very foundation of the state.

183
00:06:09,100 --> 00:06:10,500
But what does
selecting a new tribute product

184
00:06:10,700 --> 00:06:12,500
have to do with tax silver?

185
00:06:12,620 --> 00:06:13,540
Li Yunhe,

186
00:06:13,540 --> 00:06:16,540
are you suggesting
we engrave words onto the tax silver?

187
00:06:17,300 --> 00:06:18,460
But the emperor

188
00:06:18,460 --> 00:06:19,700
doesn't personally go

189
00:06:19,820 --> 00:06:21,380
to the national treasury to count taels.

190
00:06:21,380 --> 00:06:22,260
So how would you

191
00:06:22,260 --> 00:06:23,700
ever make sure he sees your message?

192
00:06:24,220 --> 00:06:26,180
To be honest,
this matter is actually quite simple.

193
00:06:26,180 --> 00:06:28,900
In clothing, food, shelter, and travel,
clothing comes first.

194
00:06:29,220 --> 00:06:30,860
Gambiered Silk is an imperial tribute.

195
00:06:31,100 --> 00:06:33,500
The amount of tax silver involved
every year is enormous.

196
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:35,020
If a new imperial tribute product

197
00:06:35,420 --> 00:06:37,500
is to be selected at this moment,

198
00:06:37,700 --> 00:06:39,300
I believe this juicy piece of meat

199
00:06:39,900 --> 00:06:41,460
will be eyed hungrily

200
00:06:41,620 --> 00:06:42,620
by the royal merchants all around.

201
00:06:42,980 --> 00:06:44,260
So what you're saying is,

202
00:06:44,260 --> 00:06:45,100
Prince Ning

203
00:06:45,100 --> 00:06:46,740
will have his eyes on this money?

204
00:06:46,740 --> 00:06:47,620
But even if Prince Ning

205
00:06:47,620 --> 00:06:48,700
sets his sights on this money,

206
00:06:48,940 --> 00:06:49,580
how can we

207
00:06:49,580 --> 00:06:50,260
find out

208
00:06:50,260 --> 00:06:51,420
where the money is moving?

209
00:06:51,580 --> 00:06:52,740
A few days ago,

210
00:06:52,740 --> 00:06:54,140
the surrounding regions
were hit by floods.

211
00:06:54,380 --> 00:06:55,340
The way I see it,

212
00:06:55,340 --> 00:06:56,300
the grain price

213
00:06:56,300 --> 00:06:57,900
at the very peak should have only
risen to about 260 coins.

214
00:06:58,580 --> 00:06:59,660
But in reality,

215
00:06:59,660 --> 00:07:00,900
the grain price shot up

216
00:07:00,900 --> 00:07:02,300
all the way to 330 coins.

217
00:07:04,140 --> 00:07:05,140
This tells us

218
00:07:05,140 --> 00:07:07,580
that a large amount of outside money
flooded into Feng City.

219
00:07:08,420 --> 00:07:09,900
So you're deducing

220
00:07:09,900 --> 00:07:12,100
that Prince Ning will make his move
right here in Feng City.

221
00:07:12,820 --> 00:07:14,500
But what does that have to do

222
00:07:14,780 --> 00:07:15,900
with Gambiered Silk?

223
00:07:16,300 --> 00:07:17,340
If Gambiered Silk

224
00:07:17,340 --> 00:07:18,980
is restored as an imperial tribute,

225
00:07:19,180 --> 00:07:20,020
then the bribe money

226
00:07:20,020 --> 00:07:21,500
used by those surrounding merchants
to grease palms

227
00:07:21,500 --> 00:07:22,900
will naturally flow back
the way it came.

228
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:25,420
But even if the silver
pooled in Feng City for bribery

229
00:07:25,420 --> 00:07:27,540
flows back out to the various regions,

230
00:07:27,900 --> 00:07:29,980
what does that have to do

231
00:07:29,980 --> 00:07:31,220
with Prince Ning's rebellion?

232
00:07:33,620 --> 00:07:35,580
Yunhe, what are you looking at me for?

233
00:07:36,300 --> 00:07:36,900
Zhao,

234
00:07:37,420 --> 00:07:39,300
if your deductions are correct,

235
00:07:39,300 --> 00:07:41,900
the Marquis of Zhennan
and Prince Ning are in cahoots.

236
00:07:42,340 --> 00:07:44,420
So when Prince Ning
stages his rebellion in Feng City,

237
00:07:44,780 --> 00:07:46,780
he'll naturally pull
the Marquis of Zhennan to his side.

238
00:07:46,780 --> 00:07:48,380
But the Marquis House,

239
00:07:48,380 --> 00:07:50,460
ever since that
rain speculation scheme a while back,

240
00:07:50,660 --> 00:07:51,060
can't even

241
00:07:51,060 --> 00:07:52,540
produce a single coin right now.

242
00:07:53,100 --> 00:07:54,900
If you were the Marquis of Zhennan,

243
00:07:55,180 --> 00:07:56,020
what would you do?

244
00:07:57,140 --> 00:07:58,540
To rise in revolt, you need grain,

245
00:07:58,540 --> 00:07:59,540
and you need money.

246
00:07:59,780 --> 00:08:01,220
If I were the Marquis of Zhennan,

247
00:08:01,220 --> 00:08:02,340
I would seize this very opportunity

248
00:08:02,660 --> 00:08:03,860
to amass wealth by any means.

249
00:08:04,020 --> 00:08:04,500
Exactly.

250
00:08:05,220 --> 00:08:06,860
During the selection
of the tribute product,

251
00:08:06,860 --> 00:08:07,900
with Feng City serving as
the gathering point for tax silver

252
00:08:07,900 --> 00:08:08,900
flooding in from all over,

253
00:08:08,900 --> 00:08:11,260
the Marquis of Zhennan will inevitably
set his sights on it.

254
00:08:11,260 --> 00:08:12,300
At that moment,

255
00:08:12,620 --> 00:08:13,580
if Gambiered Silk

256
00:08:13,580 --> 00:08:15,700
is once again chosen
as an imperial tribute,

257
00:08:16,020 --> 00:08:17,220
then all that money

258
00:08:17,220 --> 00:08:19,220
will inevitably flow right back
to where it came from.

259
00:08:19,540 --> 00:08:21,460
If Prince Ning tries to
get his hands on that wealth again,

260
00:08:22,060 --> 00:08:22,620
he'll be forced

261
00:08:22,620 --> 00:08:24,340
to spread out his concentrated forces.

262
00:08:25,220 --> 00:08:25,940
That's brilliant.

263
00:08:26,580 --> 00:08:28,540
Once Prince Ning's forces are scattered,

264
00:08:28,540 --> 00:08:29,420
it gives the imperial court

265
00:08:29,420 --> 00:08:30,860
a chance to defeat them one by one.

266
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:32,980
When the disaster relief arrives
in Feng City,

267
00:08:32,980 --> 00:08:34,620
and the dragon boat festival
is underway,

268
00:08:35,180 --> 00:08:36,820
Prince Ning will absolutely come
to Feng City in person.

269
00:08:37,180 --> 00:08:38,100
First, to seize the money.

270
00:08:38,820 --> 00:08:40,100
Second, to reclaim the edict.

271
00:08:40,900 --> 00:08:42,140
This will be our one and only chance

272
00:08:42,140 --> 00:08:43,900
to expose and thwart Prince Ning.

273
00:08:45,460 --> 00:08:46,460
But what if he

274
00:08:46,460 --> 00:08:47,220
doesn't show up?

275
00:08:48,140 --> 00:08:49,700
That will depend on

276
00:08:49,700 --> 00:08:50,700
whether Miss Xue

277
00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:52,860
is willing to step back
into the public eye.

278
00:08:53,580 --> 00:08:54,940
For my grandfather's lifelong honor,

279
00:08:54,940 --> 00:08:56,260
for peace across the realm,

280
00:08:56,820 --> 00:08:57,620
I'll do it.

281
00:08:58,060 --> 00:08:59,060
I don't fear death.

282
00:08:59,940 --> 00:09:01,500
Hmm.

283
00:09:01,500 --> 00:09:02,860
I get it.

284
00:09:03,140 --> 00:09:05,780
We're siding with the emperor.

285
00:09:23,300 --> 00:09:24,100
Li Yunhe?

286
00:09:25,460 --> 00:09:26,620
What are you doing here at the dyehouse?

287
00:09:28,140 --> 00:09:28,940
Come over here.

288
00:09:33,820 --> 00:09:34,620
Take a look at this.

289
00:09:35,780 --> 00:09:36,580
How is it?

290
00:09:39,700 --> 00:09:40,780
I came to see

291
00:09:40,780 --> 00:09:42,340
if the latest
Gambiered Silk craftsmanship

292
00:09:42,620 --> 00:09:43,740
is being strictly followed

293
00:09:43,740 --> 00:09:44,780
according to the process.

294
00:09:45,380 --> 00:09:46,660
After all, we're about to

295
00:09:46,660 --> 00:09:49,140
become an imperial tribute again.

296
00:09:49,140 --> 00:09:50,900
The quality and standard

297
00:09:50,900 --> 00:09:51,900
absolutely cannot be as uneven

298
00:09:51,900 --> 00:09:53,380
as they were before.

299
00:09:53,900 --> 00:09:54,900
Speaking of which,

300
00:09:55,820 --> 00:09:56,700
don't tell me

301
00:09:57,500 --> 00:09:59,260
you've been living here lately.

302
00:09:59,260 --> 00:10:01,060
I remember you telling me

303
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:02,580
that the quality of the first batch

304
00:10:02,860 --> 00:10:04,220
determines our reputation going forward.

305
00:10:04,660 --> 00:10:05,420
So,

306
00:10:06,020 --> 00:10:07,900
I've been here keeping an eye
on things the whole time.

307
00:10:09,540 --> 00:10:10,820
I should've realized it sooner.

308
00:10:11,340 --> 00:10:13,100
You can freely enter and leave
the Zhou Manor

309
00:10:13,100 --> 00:10:15,100
and have mastered
the core craft of Gambiered Silk.

310
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:16,180
How could you

311
00:10:16,180 --> 00:10:17,380
possibly be just a lowly hired hand?

312
00:10:19,060 --> 00:10:19,860
But

313
00:10:19,860 --> 00:10:21,740
I don't care if you're just Yu

314
00:10:21,740 --> 00:10:23,060
or the Zhou heiress.

315
00:10:24,340 --> 00:10:26,460
You're the woman I'm going to marry.

316
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:27,860
Actually,

317
00:10:28,900 --> 00:10:30,060
I think...

318
00:10:31,060 --> 00:10:31,860
Li Yunhe,

319
00:10:32,500 --> 00:10:33,540
I just think

320
00:10:33,540 --> 00:10:35,180
with all those lovely confidantes
around you,

321
00:10:35,780 --> 00:10:37,140
there's absolutely no need for you

322
00:10:37,140 --> 00:10:38,700
to set your sights only on me.

323
00:10:40,660 --> 00:10:42,460
What lovely confidantes do I have?

324
00:10:43,020 --> 00:10:44,060
What do you mean, you don't?

325
00:10:44,060 --> 00:10:45,380
Do I need to remind you?

326
00:10:45,380 --> 00:10:47,060
Take Miss Zhao Ziyao for an example.

327
00:10:47,060 --> 00:10:47,980
She has the grace of an orchid

328
00:10:47,980 --> 00:10:49,180
and the beauty of a goddess.

329
00:10:49,820 --> 00:10:50,780
Zhao Ziyao?

330
00:10:51,460 --> 00:10:52,900
She's ditzy and clueless,

331
00:10:52,900 --> 00:10:53,660
can't even recite

332
00:10:53,660 --> 00:10:54,780
her times tables properly.

333
00:10:54,780 --> 00:10:56,180
And Miss Xue?

334
00:10:56,180 --> 00:10:57,620
She's the Chancellor's granddaughter,

335
00:10:57,620 --> 00:10:59,300
a refined lady from the capital.

336
00:10:59,300 --> 00:11:00,900
She only got the courtesan title

337
00:11:01,220 --> 00:11:02,060
by hyping up

338
00:11:02,060 --> 00:11:03,340
that fake edict business.

339
00:11:04,700 --> 00:11:06,300
As for what I know,

340
00:11:06,620 --> 00:11:07,620
my silly cousin

341
00:11:07,860 --> 00:11:09,500
even wants to marry you as a concubine.

342
00:11:10,300 --> 00:11:11,540
Song Huaijin?

343
00:11:12,420 --> 00:11:13,540
Don't even get me started on her.

344
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:14,900
She's spoiled and willful,

345
00:11:14,900 --> 00:11:15,900
a shameless social climber.

346
00:11:17,300 --> 00:11:18,380
I can't even be bothered
to talk about her.

347
00:11:22,100 --> 00:11:23,180
When I was being condemned

348
00:11:23,900 --> 00:11:24,980
by the entire city,

349
00:11:24,980 --> 00:11:25,980
you were the only one

350
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:27,180
running around,

351
00:11:27,380 --> 00:11:29,140
working yourself to the bone for me,

352
00:11:29,140 --> 00:11:30,220
worn out in both body and spirit.

353
00:11:31,220 --> 00:11:32,540
I saw all of that.

354
00:11:33,020 --> 00:11:33,820
But

355
00:11:34,260 --> 00:11:35,140
I don't think

356
00:11:35,740 --> 00:11:37,580
I'm as wonderful as you think I am.

357
00:11:38,140 --> 00:11:38,700
In my eyes,

358
00:11:38,700 --> 00:11:39,780
you are the very best.

359
00:11:40,660 --> 00:11:41,420
I will marry

360
00:11:41,860 --> 00:11:42,620
none other than you.

361
00:11:43,340 --> 00:11:44,140
But...

362
00:11:45,940 --> 00:11:46,980
My mother has already accepted

363
00:11:46,980 --> 00:11:48,700
the marriage proposal
from the Marquis House.

364
00:11:51,820 --> 00:11:53,340
How could I have forgotten that?

365
00:11:53,860 --> 00:11:54,780
Wait here.

366
00:11:54,780 --> 00:11:56,220
I'll go have a word with Mrs. Zhou.

367
00:11:57,260 --> 00:11:58,140
Hold on.

368
00:11:59,180 --> 00:11:59,940
How exactly

369
00:12:00,180 --> 00:12:01,740
do you plan to convince my mother?

370
00:12:02,140 --> 00:12:03,780
I can help the Zhous' Gambiered Silk

371
00:12:04,140 --> 00:12:05,820
become an imperial tribute once again.

372
00:12:06,220 --> 00:12:07,180
Is that enough?

373
00:12:07,180 --> 00:12:07,540
But

374
00:12:07,940 --> 00:12:08,820
what would it take

375
00:12:08,820 --> 00:12:10,220
to become an imperial tribute again?

376
00:12:10,220 --> 00:12:11,220
I've received word from my sources.

377
00:12:11,340 --> 00:12:12,260
The imperial court's envoy

378
00:12:12,260 --> 00:12:13,460
has already arrived in Feng City.

379
00:12:13,740 --> 00:12:14,660
Before that happens,

380
00:12:15,140 --> 00:12:16,420
we need to hurry up

381
00:12:16,420 --> 00:12:17,140
and produce a batch

382
00:12:17,140 --> 00:12:19,020
of top-quality Gambiered Silk.

383
00:12:19,540 --> 00:12:20,420
The imperial court?

384
00:12:21,340 --> 00:12:22,620
Is this information reliable?

385
00:12:23,180 --> 00:12:24,420
My intel

386
00:12:24,660 --> 00:12:25,940
is genuine and solid,

387
00:12:26,180 --> 00:12:27,340
no cheating, no fooling.

388
00:12:27,580 --> 00:12:28,340
Wait here.

389
00:12:31,860 --> 00:12:32,820
We really need to hurry up

390
00:12:32,820 --> 00:12:34,340
and get this Gambiered Silk made.

391
00:12:41,460 --> 00:12:43,780
Get Gambiered Silk back
as an imperial tribute?

392
00:12:44,300 --> 00:12:44,940
You, of all people?

393
00:12:46,220 --> 00:12:47,020
That's right.

394
00:12:47,660 --> 00:12:48,580
Guards!

395
00:12:49,740 --> 00:12:50,740
Throw him out.

396
00:12:52,140 --> 00:12:52,940
Hold on.

397
00:12:55,220 --> 00:12:57,620
Mrs. Zhou, I'd urge you not to forget

398
00:12:57,620 --> 00:12:58,140
it was me

399
00:12:58,140 --> 00:13:00,140
who restored the core craft

400
00:13:00,140 --> 00:13:01,620
of the Zhous' Gambiered Silk.

401
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:03,140
Are you

402
00:13:03,460 --> 00:13:04,380
threatening me?

403
00:13:04,780 --> 00:13:05,740
I wouldn't dare.

404
00:13:05,940 --> 00:13:07,380
I simply wish to give you

405
00:13:07,380 --> 00:13:08,380
a chance to reconsider

406
00:13:08,380 --> 00:13:09,780
what you just said.

407
00:13:11,660 --> 00:13:12,140
Very well.

408
00:13:12,580 --> 00:13:14,260
So, let's hear it.
What's your brilliant plan?

409
00:13:16,700 --> 00:13:17,740
Oh,

410
00:13:17,780 --> 00:13:19,180
I've been on my feet all day.

411
00:13:19,340 --> 00:13:20,740
My legs are getting a bit sore.

412
00:13:22,740 --> 00:13:23,740
Get him a stool.

413
00:13:26,580 --> 00:13:27,380
Many thanks.

414
00:13:28,340 --> 00:13:29,860
Now, can you speak?

415
00:13:31,260 --> 00:13:32,380
How come my mouth suddenly feels

416
00:13:32,380 --> 00:13:33,980
so parched and dry?

417
00:13:51,140 --> 00:13:52,340
That's more like it.

418
00:13:57,020 --> 00:13:58,260
Mr. Li,

419
00:13:58,500 --> 00:13:59,820
can you speak now?

420
00:14:02,780 --> 00:14:03,340
Mrs. Zhou,

421
00:14:04,180 --> 00:14:06,420
from ancient texts and livestreams,

422
00:14:06,420 --> 00:14:07,580
I've gained an understanding

423
00:14:07,580 --> 00:14:09,260
of the core craft for Gambiered Silk.

424
00:14:09,420 --> 00:14:11,020
The reason
the Zhou family's Rustling Silk

425
00:14:11,020 --> 00:14:12,940
could become famous across the land

426
00:14:12,940 --> 00:14:13,740
was the passing down

427
00:14:13,740 --> 00:14:15,340
of the core craft.

428
00:14:16,180 --> 00:14:16,980
But unfortunately,

429
00:14:16,980 --> 00:14:18,820
the loss of that core craft

430
00:14:18,820 --> 00:14:19,620
is what led

431
00:14:19,620 --> 00:14:22,060
to the uneven quality

432
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:23,180
of our products,

433
00:14:23,180 --> 00:14:24,020
and that's why we were stripped

434
00:14:24,020 --> 00:14:25,660
of the imperial tribute status.

435
00:14:25,660 --> 00:14:26,580
However,

436
00:14:26,580 --> 00:14:27,740
since Rustling Silk

437
00:14:27,740 --> 00:14:29,540
has had
its imperial tribute status canceled,

438
00:14:29,540 --> 00:14:30,700
that means opportunity has come knocking

439
00:14:30,700 --> 00:14:31,580
for our Gambiered Silk.

440
00:14:31,580 --> 00:14:32,340
Hmm.

441
00:14:32,500 --> 00:14:34,940
I'm aware of everything you've said.

442
00:14:35,460 --> 00:14:37,340
I wonder what your plan is, Mr. Li.

443
00:14:39,140 --> 00:14:41,420
Special problems
call for special treatment

444
00:14:41,420 --> 00:14:42,620
and special solutions.

445
00:14:42,620 --> 00:14:43,420
Li Yunhe,

446
00:14:43,900 --> 00:14:44,860
you're indeed quite capable,

447
00:14:45,460 --> 00:14:46,940
I'll give you that.

448
00:14:47,220 --> 00:14:49,020
You even managed to revive

449
00:14:49,020 --> 00:14:50,580
the core technique of Rustling Silk.

450
00:14:50,580 --> 00:14:51,460
But

451
00:14:51,460 --> 00:14:53,180
becoming an imperial tribute

452
00:14:53,660 --> 00:14:54,860
isn't something you can achieve

453
00:14:54,860 --> 00:14:56,140
through quality alone.

454
00:14:56,420 --> 00:14:57,980
I'll lay my cards
on the table right here.

455
00:14:58,740 --> 00:15:00,380
If you can truly get Gambiered Silk

456
00:15:00,380 --> 00:15:02,340
back on the imperial tribute list,

457
00:15:02,540 --> 00:15:03,900
I would willingly marry you

458
00:15:03,940 --> 00:15:04,940
as a concubine.

459
00:15:06,820 --> 00:15:07,500
That won't be necessary.

460
00:15:07,780 --> 00:15:09,140
Being my concubine? Really unnecessary.

461
00:15:09,540 --> 00:15:10,740
You're not my type.

462
00:15:12,340 --> 00:15:13,020
I know

463
00:15:13,540 --> 00:15:14,500
that your only goal

464
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:15,940
is to marry my daughter.

465
00:15:16,340 --> 00:15:17,500
But as you also know,

466
00:15:17,500 --> 00:15:18,340
I've already agreed

467
00:15:18,340 --> 00:15:19,500
to the marriage proposal
from the Marquis House.

468
00:15:19,500 --> 00:15:20,660
As for the Marquis House,

469
00:15:20,660 --> 00:15:21,620
please rest easy, Mrs. Zhou.

470
00:15:21,620 --> 00:15:22,940
I'll handle that myself.

471
00:15:23,380 --> 00:15:24,660
I've come here today

472
00:15:24,660 --> 00:15:25,100
simply to obtain

473
00:15:25,100 --> 00:15:26,500
one promise from you, Mrs. Zhou.

474
00:15:31,820 --> 00:15:32,340
Very well.

475
00:15:32,660 --> 00:15:33,580
Li Yunhe,

476
00:15:33,820 --> 00:15:35,060
if you can get Gambiered Silk

477
00:15:35,060 --> 00:15:36,460
back as an imperial tribute

478
00:15:36,460 --> 00:15:38,700
and resolve the marriage proposal
from the Marquis House,

479
00:15:38,700 --> 00:15:39,500
then I'll consent

480
00:15:39,500 --> 00:15:41,420
to betroth Zhou Xingyu to you.

481
00:15:43,460 --> 00:15:44,260
Well then,

482
00:15:45,180 --> 00:15:46,060
it's settled.

483
00:15:46,740 --> 00:15:47,980
Looking forward to your good news.

484
00:15:57,700 --> 00:15:58,580
So, does that mean

485
00:15:59,100 --> 00:16:00,460
Prince Ning has already arrived?

486
00:16:01,260 --> 00:16:02,660
Yes, Your Majesty.

487
00:16:03,100 --> 00:16:05,380
According to the latest intelligence
from our covert operatives,

488
00:16:05,380 --> 00:16:07,700
Prince Ning
has secretly arrived in Feng City.

489
00:16:07,940 --> 00:16:08,860
And...

490
00:16:09,620 --> 00:16:10,540
Go on.

491
00:16:10,700 --> 00:16:12,580
And word has come back

492
00:16:13,020 --> 00:16:15,500
that the Marquis of Zhennan has
also returned from the military camp.

493
00:16:16,340 --> 00:16:17,820
He even hosted a banquet
in Prince Ning's honor.

494
00:16:17,820 --> 00:16:18,700
Such insolence!

495
00:16:49,340 --> 00:16:52,940
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

496
00:16:53,100 --> 00:16:56,300
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

497
00:16:56,820 --> 00:16:59,540
♪Who took the March rain♪

498
00:16:59,780 --> 00:17:03,140
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

499
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:06,300
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

500
00:17:06,460 --> 00:17:09,660
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

501
00:17:10,540 --> 00:17:16,460
♪Needle and thread
stitch away the marks of time♪

502
00:17:16,500 --> 00:17:19,940
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

503
00:17:20,180 --> 00:17:23,020
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

504
00:17:23,180 --> 00:17:25,460
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

505
00:17:25,460 --> 00:17:29,660
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

506
00:17:29,740 --> 00:17:33,020
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

507
00:17:33,180 --> 00:17:36,300
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

508
00:17:36,820 --> 00:17:39,740
♪In this life I'd be a cloud-tailor♪

509
00:17:39,900 --> 00:17:46,420
♪Never failing the stars,
nor failing you♪

510
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:16,220
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

511
00:18:16,460 --> 00:18:19,620
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

512
00:18:20,220 --> 00:18:22,940
♪Who took the March rain♪

513
00:18:23,140 --> 00:18:26,460
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

514
00:18:26,860 --> 00:18:29,740
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

515
00:18:29,820 --> 00:18:33,540
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

516
00:18:33,580 --> 00:18:36,860
♪Warp and weft entwine,
one shuttle, one dream♪

517
00:18:36,860 --> 00:18:39,820
♪As seasons change♪

518
00:18:39,820 --> 00:18:43,460
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

519
00:18:43,460 --> 00:18:46,300
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

520
00:18:46,380 --> 00:18:48,940
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

521
00:18:48,940 --> 00:18:53,020
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

522
00:18:53,020 --> 00:18:56,340
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

523
00:18:56,340 --> 00:19:00,060
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

524
00:19:00,460 --> 00:19:03,580
♪Washing away
a lifetime of wear and tear♪

525
00:19:03,580 --> 00:19:06,460
♪Only for you♪

526
00:19:06,460 --> 00:19:10,060
♪On the street of golden honors,
the music rises♪

527
00:19:10,180 --> 00:19:12,940
♪The moon moves west
beyond the pavilion♪

528
00:19:13,060 --> 00:19:15,620
♪Wine runs dry, yet the revelry lingers♪

529
00:19:15,620 --> 00:19:19,700
♪In silk, I seek a kindred soul♪

530
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:23,020
♪The rain has ceased,
clouds begin to clear♪

531
00:19:23,060 --> 00:19:26,420
♪The fragrant silk billows
under the low-hung stars♪

532
00:19:27,260 --> 00:19:32,940
♪I'd cut the clouds and morning glow
to drape over you♪

533
00:19:34,020 --> 00:19:38,140
♪A single bolt of silk becomes♪

534
00:19:39,420 --> 00:19:43,940
♪Your wedding gown♪
